item.title: Lost in Da Lat
item.dc:creator: Nam Vũ
item.content:encoded:
Lost in Da Lat

Da Lat (Vietnamese: Đà Lạt, is the capital of Lâm Đồng Province and the largest city of Central Highlands region. The city is located 1,500 m (4,900 ft) above sea level on the Langbian Plateau.
